summary:
Keith Urban covering ‘Better Man’ from the [remorseful] male’s perspective made me feel things.
I’ve always imagined Keith’s...
caption:
Keith Urban covering ‘Better Man’ from the [remorseful] male’s perspective made me feel things.
I’ve always imagined Keith’s song ‘Stupid Boy’ * as the other persons perspective on a relationship like the one portrayed in ‘Better Man’, so yeah, I dig it.

* the theme of the song and these specific lyrics
“You stupid boy
Oh, I’m the same old, same old stupid boy
It took a while for her to figure out she could run
But when she did, she was long gone, long gone”

summary: Thank you, @taylorswift for the four shows I had the privilege of attending: Glendale, Pasadena 1 & 2, and Seattle! I never...
caption:
Thank you, @taylorswift for the four shows I had the privilege of attending: Glendale, Pasadena 1 & 2, and Seattle! I never would have imagined being able to go to four shows! I love you, and I’m so thankful that I got to sit on the floor and collect confetti this tour, see you in multiple stadiums (!!!), meet so many Swifties, and most of all, see you preform four times! I love you, I love you, I love you.
Forever & Always,
Erin
@taylornation
